{"title":"LJJ 学二项式定理 · 二","time_limit":1500,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["矩阵","DFT（含 NTT）及FFT","数学"],"operation":{"submit":"https://loj.ac/problem/6575#submit_code","submissions":"https://loj.ac/submissions?problem_id=6575","statistics":"https://loj.ac/problem/6575/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://loj.ac/problem/6575/testdata","discussion":"https://loj.ac/discussion/problem/6575"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"LJJ 学完了二项式定理，觉得这式子不够优美，于是他随手写下了一个他认为优美的式子：\r\n$$\r\n\\begin {aligned}\r\n\\left(\\sum_{i=0}^{\\left\\lfloor \\frac{n}{m-1}\\right\\rfloor } {n+i\\choose m\\cdot i}\\right) \\bmod p\r\n\\end{aligned}\r\n$$\r\n其中 $ n\\choose i $ 表示 $ \\cfrac{n!}{i!(n-i)!} $。\r\n\r\n然而他并不会计算这个式子。你能帮帮他吗？\r\n"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一行三个整数 $n, m, p$。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出仅一行：一个整数 $\\text{ans}$ 表示将 $n, m, p$ 的值代入式子得到的答案。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入 1\r\n```plain\r\n1000 20 10007\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出 1\r\n```plain\r\n8319\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入 2\r\n```plain\r\n1000000 50 100000000\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出 2\r\n```plain\r\n36114455\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输入 3\r\n```plain\r\n1000000000000000000 1000 123456789\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出 3\r\n```plain\r\n29514861\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于所有数据，均满足：$n\\ge 1,\\ 1<m\\le n+1,\\ p\\le 10^9$。\r\n\r\n|   测试点编号   |  $n\\le$   | $m\\le$ |    特殊性质     |\r\n| :------------: | :-------: | :----: | :-------------: |\r\n|   $1\\sim 4$   |  $1000$   | $1000$ |       无        |\r\n|     $5,6$     |  $10^6$   | $1000$ |   $p$ 为质数    |\r\n|     $7,8$     |  $10^6$   | $1000$ |       无        |\r\n|  $9\\sim 12$  | $10^{18}$ |  $50$  |       无        |\r\n| $13\\sim 16$ | $10^{18}$ | $1000$ |       无        |\r\n| $17\\sim 20$  | $10^{18}$ | $5000$ | $p = 998244353$ |"}]}